  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will address a gap in the literature and advance the field of minority men's
      health. Specifically, it will be the first randomized controlled trial of resistance exercise
      as a dual intervention for depression symptoms and CVD risk reduction with depressed Black
      men.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
